</span><span class="lnt">6
</span><span class="lnt">7
</span><span class="lnt">8
</span><span class="lnt">9
</span></code></pre></td>
<td class="lntd">
<pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-shell" data-lang="shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">df -k <span class="p">|</span> grep -e <span class="s1">&#39;lv&#39;</span> <span class="p">|</span> awk <span class="s1">&#39;{ print $4 &#34; &#34; $7 }&#39;</span> <span class="p">|</span> <span class="k">while</span> <span class="nb">read</span> output<span class="p">;</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">do</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="nv">$output</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nv">usep</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="k">$(</span><span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="nv">$output</span> <span class="p">|</span> awk <span class="s1">&#39;{ print $1}&#39;</span> <span class="p">|</span> cut -d<span class="s1">&#39;%&#39;</span> -f1 <span class="k">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nv">partition</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="k">$(</span><span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="nv">$output</span> <span class="p">|</span> awk <span class="s1">&#39;{ print $2 }&#39;</span> <span class="k">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">if</span> <span class="o">[</span> <span class="nv">$usep</span> -ge <span class="m">90</span> <span class="o">]</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="k">then</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="nb">echo</span> <span class="s2">&#34;Verifique o diretorio &#34;</span><span class="nv">$partition</span><span class="s2">&#34; com (</span><span class="nv">$usep</span><span class="s2">%) de uso no servidor </span><span class="k">$(</span>hostname<span class="k">)</span><span class="s2">&#34;</span> <span class="p">|</span> mail -s <span class="s2">&#34;Alerta! Disco excedido em </span><span class="nv">$usep</span><span class="s2">%&#34;</span> seu_email@provedor.com
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">fi</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="k">done</span></span></span></code></pre></td></tr></table>
</div>
</div>]]></description></item><item><title>Atalhos úteis para a linha de comando</title><link>https://sidneiweber.com.br/atalhos-uteis-para-a-linha-de-comando/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2015 15:38:45 -0300</pubDate><author>Sidnei Weber</author><guid>https://sidneiweber.com.br/atalhos-uteis-para-a-linha-de-comando/</guid><description><![CDATA[<table>
